mixin welcome
  div.splash
      h1 Contribution Pilot
      p Welcome to our contribution pilot study (formerly "Interdisciplinary Programming"). We're studying how the community can solve problems and build new tools together.
  div
      div.content.content-contrast.is-center
          div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-link
              h3.content-subhead What we're doing
              p
                | In this four month pilot, we'll be helping the community partner together to solve problems and build new tools.
            div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-users
              h3.content-subhead How you can help
              p
                | This is open to all! We need designers, developers, scientists, communicators and more to collaborate on projects.
            div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-heart
